                        <interp inst="t18360613-name-154" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN KEMPSTER</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I saw him take it out—I told a friend my suspicions, and had no sooner spoken than be took up the cost tail, and took the handkerchief out.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> He asked me to give the handkerchief up. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> I did not.</p>
